            "side": "right",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Knowledge / Research Template\n\nCanonical v1 authoring loop:\n- frame a research `question`\n- anchor the main `concept`\n- attach a `source`\n- capture `evidence`\n- state a `claim`\n- synthesize into a `summary`\n\nThe bridge row below is the authoritative class surface for this template.",
